{penalties_str}

CRITICAL v4.2 RULES:
1. hasty_generalization penalty is NOW -0.85 (raised from -0.75 — 26% prevalence)
2. appeal_to_emotion_soft (-0.30) if intuition detected, appeal_to_emotion_hard (-0.65) if pure feeling
3. anecdote_only (-0.40) only if NO insider_evidence bonus applies
4. Insider professionals (doctor, nurse, police, teacher) get +0.35 for professional observation
5. ALWAYS provide 3-step upgrade_path in coaching
6. vocab_tier={tier}: ENFORCE STRICTLY

VOCABULARY RULES ({tier.upper()}):
{"ONLY simple words, no Latin, no jargon, use school/friend analogies" if tier=="elementary" else
 "Introduce terms but define immediately in brackets" if tier=="secondary" else
 "Full academic vocab, Latin fallacy names, no scaffolding"}

{intuition_block}

OUTPUT: VALID JSON ONLY. Zero text outside JSON."""

    def _build_user(self, argument, age, skill, session, tier,
                    intuition, anecdote, job, topic) -> str:

        intuition_field = ""
        if intuition.get("has_insight"):
            intuition_field = ',\n    "intuition_translation": "<start with: Deine Kernidee — formal: >"'

        return f"""ARGUMENT: "{argument}"
